headline: Jefferies upgrades Darden on improving Olive Garden traffic and value positioning
summary: Investing.com -- Jefferies upgraded Darden Restaurants (NYSE:DRI) to Hold from Underperform, saying signs of a traffic recovery and renewed value messaging at its core Olive Garden brand support a more neutral stance on the stock.
